law.catch_line: Chiropractor may sign death certificates and other legal documents.
law.text: Any person licensed under this chapter may sign death certificates and sign and execute all legal documents and certificates with the same authority as members of other schools or systems of treatment.
law.history: Repealed 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2643a-14.
